        <!-- RECENT CASE STUDY SECTION (Kept for content reference, but not in header nav) -->
        <section id="recent-case-study">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="animate-on-scroll">Recent Case Study: From Struggling to Soaring</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">See how a data-driven, client-centric SEO strategy delivered dramatic results in just two months.</p>
                <div class="recent-case-study-content animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                    <h3>The Challenge: Stagnant Growth & Untapped Potential</h3>
                    <p>I recently rescued a professional services company with locations in Northern Virginia and Chesterfield, Michigan, that had been struggling for 8 months. While they had decent branded traffic, they couldn't drive organic relevant traffic that actually generated revenue or leads - stuck at only <strong>1,200 monthly organic sessions</strong> with keywords around <strong>position 47</strong> and just <strong>22 leads per month</strong>.</p>

                    <h3>My Approach: Deep Dive & Targeted Action</h3>
                    <p>My approach started with a comprehensive audit covering technical performance, content quality, keyword opportunities, website response rates, layout issues, and CRO optimization gaps. I conducted deep competitor analysis to understand what was working in their local markets, studying demographics and user psychology in both Northern Virginia and Michigan to craft content matching search intent. Most importantly, I dove deep into their business niche to understand exactly what their potential customers are searching for and how they make purchasing decisions.</p>

                    <p>Within the first 3 weeks, I fixed critical technical issues, including slow load times, missing local schema markup, and mobile optimization problems. Then I launched an aggressive content marketing strategy, publishing 3-5 highly informative blogs weekly, targeting well-researched, high-search-volume topics specific to their service areas. I focused on local search optimization and targeted outreach without aggressive backlinking, instead emphasizing quality content that addressed real customer pain points in both markets.</p>

                    <h3>The Transformation: Dramatic Results in 2 Months</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Organic Traffic:</strong> Exploded from <strong>1,200 to 4,164 monthly sessions (+247%)</strong>.</li>
                        <li><strong>Keyword Rankings:</strong> Jumped from <strong>position 47 to position 8</strong> for relevant terms.</li>
                        <li><strong>Organic Leads:</strong> Increased from <strong>22 to 127 per month (+477%)</strong>.</li>
                        <li><strong>Monthly Revenue:</strong> Grew from <strong>$18,400 to $51,560 (+180% ROI)</strong>.</li>
                        <li><strong>Conversion Rate:</strong> Doubled from <strong>1.8% to 3.8%</strong> because the traffic was now highly relevant and purchase-ready.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>This proves that understanding your client's business niche deeply, combined with strategic local content marketing, can reverse months of poor performance in weeks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- HARO & LINK BUILDING SECTION -->
        <section id="haro-section">
            <div class="container animate-on-scroll">
